'''Oroboro''' was the name of a [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] hive on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]. Oroboro meant "our home" in the Killik language and was a region located across the northern steppes of Alderaan known as the [[Castle Lands]].<ref name="Dark Nest I: The Joiner King">''[[Dark Nest I: The Joiner King]]''</ref> [[Oroboro Killik Caverns]] could be found within the [[Kaamos Territory]] around [[3643 BBY]]. [[Vector Hyllus]] and [[Pabel Alde]] were [[Joiner]]s of the hive.

